OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain, heavy
OL,6,Fat times, edging slowly eastwards
OL,7,Fthrough the evening and overnight.
OL,8,FSome snow possible is also over the
OL,9,FScottish mountains. Clear spells and
OL,10,Fblustery showers following. Windy for
OL,11,Fall, with gales in the northwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain across central and
OL,14,Feastern areas soon clearing. Showers
OL,15,Ffollowing for most, these heavy in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland and western Scotland.
OL,17,FWindy with coastal gales in the west.
OL,18,FTemperatures near average.
